==Abstract==

The following proposal is based on BMIP-0002. This standard provides asset definitions of other chain assets on Bytom

==Motivation==

In order to support the standard definition of the assets of other chains on Bytom, the identification is added based on the JSON format defined by BMIP-0002.

==Specification==

===Asset Definition===

The following specifications use syntax of standard JSON schema

Add 5 identifiers to the description in JSON format of BMIP-0002 asset definition

====description====

Include an asset description consisting of arbitrary key-value data - e.g. <code>{"Email":"foo@bar.com"}</code>

=====chain_id=====

标识链的唯一性，内容格式：ID+federationSig+openFederationSig 。对内容进行hash得到chain_id。

ID参考BIP44的的coin编码

签名的内容是指定高度的blockhash

=====genesis_hash=====

主链创世块hash，分叉链是分叉后第一个区块的hash

=====federation_public_keys=====

在bytom上发行资产的主链联邦地址的公钥

=====require_sign_quorum=====

主链上联邦签名的个数

=====issue_asset_action=====

资产是什么行为发行的资产，如果等于cross_chain表示是其他主链在bytom上发送的资产，在vapor上验证交易时验证是否开放网关的签名